Ellen Gerstell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellen_Gerstell 0 Ellen Gerstell (born October 22, 1954) is an American voice actress. She is most known for providing the voice of Rapture in Jem and Mihoshi Kuramitsu in the Tenchi Muyo! franchise. Ellen_Gerstell ( born October_22_,_1954 ) is an_American_voice_actress .
